Dummy Phecode Map 1.2 with ICD-10 codes (beta) file path

Source: R/dummy.R
dummy_icd10_phecode_map_path.Rd

Returns the file path to a dummy Phecode Map 1.2 with ICD-10 codes (beta) csv file (full version may be downloaded from phewascatalog.org).

Usage

dummy_icd10_phecode_map_path()

Value

A string.

See also

Other Dummy data: build_all_lkps_maps_dummy(), dummy_all_lkps_maps_db(), dummy_all_lkps_maps_path(), dummy_caliber_dir_path(), dummy_clinical_events_tidy(), dummy_phecode_lkp_path(), dummy_ukb_codings_path(), read_all_lkps_maps_dummy(), read_icd10_phecode_map_dummy(), read_phecode_lkp_dummy(), read_ukb_codings_dummy()

Examples

dummy_icd10_phecode_map_path()
#> [1] "/home/runner/work/_temp/Library/codeminer/extdata/dummy_Phecode_map_v1_2_icd10_beta.csv"
